}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#2a6c71744efc65688bceed1492ccbc1b>.
<#2a6c71744efc65688bceed1492ccbc1b> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/728cbad6-b063-40de-b07c-4ce027f4614b>;
