}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#2fac3a9eb05ed928f6a8aac9d2ab8c72>.
<#2fac3a9eb05ed928f6a8aac9d2ab8c72> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/9ae566f3-b4a8-4de2-8ed1-444acb67cc78>;
