<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#fd94e060f1bce8f7c6267669b1456f6b>.
<#fd94e060f1bce8f7c6267669b1456f6b> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/545f7280-7d15-11ed-a51b-432755aaeed3>;
