<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#265b9b0dcba1d8f5fde3cdd6b956f82e>.
<#265b9b0dcba1d8f5fde3cdd6b956f82e> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://doi.org/10.5878/d9ck-bd78>;
