    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Target Tailored Forest Damage Inventory (TFDI) - Damage by bark beetles on Norway spruce in Götaland and Svealand 2020"@en, "Nationell Riktad Skogsskadeinventering (NRS) - Barkborreskador på gran i Götaland och Svealand 2020"@sv;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__2888.
