    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Target Tailored Forest Damage Inventory (TFDI) - Damage by bark beetles on Norway spruce in the county of Västernorrland and eastern Jämtland 2016"@en, "Nationell Riktad Skogsskadeinventering (NRS) - Barkborreskador på gran i Västernorrlands län och östra Jämtland 2016"@sv;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__816.
_:b0__816 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2016-10-02"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
