    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2025-02-28T14:15:23.278058Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Data för artikeln: Modelling metal uptake by selected vegetables from urban soils in Europe: Uncovering key soil factors using Partial Least Squares Regression (PLS-R)"@sv, "Data for the paper: Modelling metal uptake by selected vegetables from urban soils in Europe: Uncovering key soil factors using Partial Least Squares Regression (PLS-R)"@en;
