<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#c170cb36b20ccdf296e7eac6c75984f2>.
<#c170cb36b20ccdf296e7eac6c75984f2> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://doi.org/10.5878/kbt4-b102>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-11T06:23:27.376Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#c170cb36b20ccdf296e7eac6c75984f2> {
<https://doi.org/10.5878/kbt4-b102> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "bacteria"@en, "bakterier"@sv, "mikrobiota"@sv, "microbiome"@en, "mjölksyrebakterier"@sv, "lactic acid bacteria"@en, "Amerikansk yngelröta"@sv, "American foulbrood"@en, "Paenibacillus larvae"@sv, "Paenibacillus larvae"@en, "apis mellifera linnaeus, 1758"@en, "bifidobacterium asteroides scardovi & trovatelli, 1969"@en, "bifidobacterium coryneforme (ex scardovi & trovatelli, 1969) biavati et al., 1982"@en, "Apilactobacillus apinorum"@en, "Lactobacillus kullabergensis"@en, "Bifidobacteria asteroides"@en, "Lactobacillus apis"@en, "Bombilactobacillus mellis"@en, "Lactobacillus melliventris"@en, "Bifidobacteria coryneforme"@en, "Lactobacillus helsingborgensis"@en, "Apilactobacillus kunkeei"@en, "Lactobacillus kimbladii"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__9707.
_:b0__9707 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/principalInvestigator>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/31289027de5912baf3060fffec95574d>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Attribution>.
<https://doi.org/10.5878/kbt4-b102> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2021002817>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "I denna studie analyserades DNA extraherat från honungsbin med hjälp av qPCR för närvaron och kvantiteten av olika honungsbispecifika mjölksyrabakterier. Syftet var att undersöka om det finns skillnader i sammansättningen av mjölksyrabakterier hos bin från bisamhällen och bigårdar med eller utan sjukdomen amerikansk yngelröta.  I datafilen \"Sample_info\" hittas bakgrundsinformation för de individuella proverna, filen innehåller 7 kolumner och 42 rader. I datafilen  \"Data_LAB_AFB_in_Sweden\" hittas Cq-värden för alla prover och bakterier, filen innehåller 11 kolumner och 493 rader.  I filen \"Bactdilutions\" hittas bakteriekoncentrationer och Cq-värden för seriespädningar av bakterierna som proverna analyserats för, filen innehåller 3 kolumner och 47 rader."@sv, "In this study DNA extracted from honeybees was analysed using qPCR for the presence and quantity of different honeybee-specific lactic acid bacteria. The aim was to investigate if presence of the disease American foulbrood in the beehive or in the apiary affects honeybees composition of lactic acid bacteria. In the data file \"Sample_info\" background information for the individual samples is found, the data file contains 7 columns and 42 rows. In the data file \"Data_LAB_AFB_in_Sweden\" Cq values are found for all samples and bacteria, the data file contains 11 columns and 493 rows. In the data file \"Bactdilutions\", bacterial concentrations and Cq values for serial dilutions of the bacteria the samples were analyzed for are found. The data file “Bactdilutions” contains 3 columns and 47 rows."@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://sws.geonames.org/2661886>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/51114b511532c3a2185d2769d45f9a7f>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://doi.org/10.5878/kbt4-b102#distribution>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2024-04-19T12:29:50.622049Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://doi.org/10.5878/kbt4-b102>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2024-04-19T12:29:50.622049Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Data för: Lactic acid bacteria in Swedish honeybees during outbreaks of American Foulbrood"@sv, "Data from: Lactic acid bacteria in Swedish honeybees during outbreaks of American Foulbrood"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__6448.
_:b0__6448 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2018-06"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2018-05"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://doi.org/10.5878/kbt4-b102> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

