    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Kod i MATLAB r2022b, innehållande relevant data, för tidskriftsartikeln: Pons, \"The self-oscillation paradox in the flight motor of D. melanogaster\", Journal of the Royal Society Interface, 2023. Koden är kommenterad, och inkluderar passningsanalys, självsvängningsanalys och datorsymboliska beräkningar"@sv, "Code in MATLAB r2022b, containing relevant data, for the journal article:  Pons, \"The self-oscillation paradox in the flight motor of D. melanogaster\", Journal of the Royal Society Interface, 2023. Code is annotated, and includes fitting analysis, self-oscillation (eigenvalue) analysis, and computer symbolic computations"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/6901e8091926081be794ab8f35b2327b>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://doi.org/10.5878/dq5w-x472#distribution>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2023-10-20T11:44:18.371519Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://doi.org/10.5878/dq5w-x472>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2025-06-05T11:35:45.995668Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Data om: \"The self-oscillation paradox in the flight motor of D. melanogaster\""@sv, "Data for: \"The self-oscillation paradox in the flight motor of D. melanogaster\""@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TECH>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#2d1577ec3cd3ba9cdd4e3fd7d6c747df>.
<#2d1577ec3cd3ba9cdd4e3fd7d6c747df> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://doi.org/10.5878/dxqw-6y59>;
