_:b0__2958 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2023-02-20"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2018-09-28"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://doi.org/10.5878/7eww-g857> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
