<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#68ff9da64732875fc6543de8f9c5ebd4>.
<#68ff9da64732875fc6543de8f9c5ebd4> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/U07485>;
